Syntax: mindoverbody

Uses focused mental discipline to trigger healing over time during combat.
By concentrating your mind on physical recovery, you can sustain yourself
through ongoing damage. This skill is available to Pugilist-line characters
(Monk, Brawler, Martial Artist).

Effects when activated:
  - Costs energy (via the energy system, cost is higher if cooldown is active).
  - Grants +1 chi.
  - Applies a healing-over-time (HOT) affect lasting 3 combat rounds.
    Healing amount is based on: Pugilist level + (Monk * 2) + (Brawler * 2)
    + (Martial Artist * 5).
  - Activates a 15-round cooldown preventing reuse.

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Must have energy available.
  - Must have the Mind Over Body skill learned.

See also: shelp mind over body chakra healing light restoration
